<br>
How could Poseidon be feeling like this, especially to one whom Zeus held in high esteem? It happened on that day the goodess Aphrodite was caught fornicating with Ares, the war God, in Hephaestus' own bed. The other God's laughed and made jokes about themselves being in Ares position. Poseidon however felt the same turn-on as the others yet acted to be bereft of such desires. The God was never the same after that day, after seeing the goddess of love in bed with Ares.<br>
<br>
When Aphrodite closed her eyes he looked upon her perfect body, from her small feet, her thick legs and hips, small waist and breasts, to her rounded, narrow shoulders and unflawed face. She then spoke, and the god heard a whisper in his head telling him to make a move.<br>
<br>
Poseidon let out a fake laugh and said to her, &quot;If it is boring what is it that you would do to spice up the moment?' <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xgoddessoflovex>XGoddess of LoveX</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(2/9/03 4:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=295.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What do you want to do Love Goddess!</span><hr size=1> Playing with a curled blonde tress of hair, blue eyes spotted on the wall, the Goddess of Love answered quickly.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'm picturing, a nice warm bath, with rose petals, and candles all around.&quot; She took in a breath, letting her chest rise and then fall. She repositioned herself in her chair. Her legs hooked themselves over the right arm rest while her back leaned against the left one. She let her index and pointer fingers of her right hand run up and down the side of the back of the chair, in a teasing manner. She scrunched her nose, closed her eyes, and threw her head back playfully. &quot;And a pair of strong hands massaging my shoulders..ever so...&quot; She turned her head to look to Poseidon. She really hadn't taken it into consideration, who, excatly she was talking to. She spun herself back around, sitting in the normal way. Legs crossed back straight up against the back of the chair.<br>
&quot;Oh, Poseidon. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>How</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>are</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>you</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->...&quot;  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=poseidonkofc>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 349<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(4/10/03 7:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=295.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.theoi.com/image/K2.1Poseidon.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Emotional!</span><hr size=1> The ancient god said that he was doing well to Aphrodite after she put on quite a show for him unknowingly. The God rose from his chair and fixed his crown which had sunk slightly in an uneven tilt on his head. &quot;Oh Aphrodite...&quot; he said in an almost longing voice for something he could not have &quot;..you make me regret the day I married!&quot; His eyes gazed undauntingly upon her and than his words almost stung his heart as he realized what he had just made manifest. He could not believe it and his eyes quivered in a moment of emotional distraut. <br>
<br>
Then the god bade the beautiful seductress farewell as he passed away from the glorious halls of Olympus to his own wondrous halls in the sea. <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#FFFF33>- </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite>Amazons Unite</a><font color=#FFFF33> - </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23>The Olympian Gods</a> <font color=#FFFF33> - </font><a href="http://pub163.ezboard.com/bmythicalodysseyforum">Home</a><font color=#FFFF33> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.3m<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

